Required packages:
------------------
* apache2
* apache2-mod_perl
* sqlite
* perl-DBI
* perl-DBD-SQLite
* perl-Crypt-SSLeay
* perl-Config-IniFiles
* perl-XML-Parser
* perl-XML-Writer
* perl-libwww-perl
* perl-IO-Zlib
* perl-URI
* perl-TimeDate

Setup
-----

enhance /etc/sysconfig/apache2 APACHE_MODULES with "perl"

call: make install_all

call: rcapache2 start

